'''Asian Luge Cup''' is annual [[luge]] competition for Asian countries, which held since 1998. There are men's and women's single events and men's double event. All editions of Asian Luge Cup held by [[Spiral (bobsleigh, luge, and skeleton)|Spiral bobsleigh luge, and skeleton track]] at [[Nagano City|Nagano]], [[Japan]].

