{{Infobox company | name = Parcel Direct Ireland | logo = [[File:Parcel Direct Logo.png|Parcel Direct Logo]] | type = [[Private company|Private]] | founded = 2014 | founder = Stephen O' Sullivan | area_served = Worldwide | key_people = Stephen O' Sullivan | industry = [[Courier]] | num_employees = 10 | website = {{URL|parceldirect.ie}} | location = [[Ireland]] }}
'''Parcel Direct Ireland''' is a courier service provider used by the general public and small and medium businesses in Ireland. Parcel Direct Ireland has formed shipping partnerships with logistics providers including [[FedEx]], [[United Parcel Service|UPS]], [[TNT Express|TNT]], [[DHL Express|DHL]], [[Dynamic Parcel Distribution|DPD]], and [[General Logistics Systems|GLS]]. Parcel Direct Ireland purchases service at wholesale rates and re-sells the services to their consumer and business customers.
The company was founded by Stephen O’ Sullivan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.ie/business/irish/john-hourican-banks-prize-31371254.html|title=Time Saving Deliveries|website=Irish Independent}}</ref> in 2014. Based in a head office in [[Cork City]], Parcel Direct Ireland offers courier services to consumers and small businesses throughout Ireland. They have also focused on the large number of Irish citizens living and relocating abroad.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.joe.ie/uncategorized/this-company-is-making-it-easier-for-irish-mammies-to-send-care-packages-abroad-501803|title=Generation Emigration|website=JOE}}</ref>
In 2015 the company launched its eCommerce solutions in line with the Government National Digital Strategy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dccae.gov.ie/en-ie/communications/topics/Digital-Strategy/Pages/default.aspx|title=Digital Media Strategy|website=Department of Communications}}</ref> to get more businesses throughout Ireland selling online, including working with the [[County and City Enterprise Board|Local Enterprise Boards]].
In 2016, Parcel Direct Ireland was nominated for the Blacknight SME Awards <ref>{{cite web|url=http://smeawards.ie/finalists/|title=SME Awards|website=SME Awards}}</ref> for its developments.
